Package commands

package commands
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Clear
    Command to clear the entire collection.
    Command
    Abstract base class for commands.
    CommandList
    A list of commands available in the program
    ExecuteScript
    Command to execute a script from a file.
    Exit
    Command to exit the program.
    FilterStartsWithName
    Command to filter all elements and return all elements starts with written name.
    Help
    Command to print a description of using of all commands
    Info
    Command to print an information about collection in memory
    Insert
    Command to initialize creation of new Worker instance and insert it to a collection.
    RemoveAllByEndDate
    The RemoveGreater command removes all elements in the collection managed by CollectionManager which has the same end date as given
    RemoveAllByStartDate
    The RemoveGreater command removes all elements in the collection managed by CollectionManager which has the same start date as given
    RemoveGreater
    Command to remove all elements from the collection which has field greater that the specified one.
    RemoveGreaterKey
    Command to remove all elements from the collection which has key greater that the specified one.
    RemoveLowerKey
    Command to remove all elements from the collection which has key lower that the specified one.
    Save
    Command to write all workers from collection to file
    Show
    Command to show all workers containing in collection
